article_id:238,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing the Next Summon Showcase, Ardent Admirers!,image_path:,message:<div>The next Summon Showcase, Ardent Admirers, kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550124000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The showcase features limited-time adventurers and wyrmprints, as well as new non-limited dragons and wyrmprints. Featured adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints also have an increased appearance rate!<br><br>Note: The newly-added 5★ dragon, Prometheus (flame), and the 4★ wyrmprint, Entwined Flames, will continue to appear in summon showcases after this showcase.</div><div><br></div><div>Limited-Time Adventurers and Wyrmprints:</div><div><br></div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Hildegarde (Valentine&#39;s version) (flame/staff)</div><div>4★ Ezelith (Valentine&#39;s version) (flame/bow)</div><div>3★ Orion (Valentine&#39;s version) (flame/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>■Wyrmprints</div><div>5★ The Chocolatiers</div><div>5★ The Rose Prince</div><div>3★ To My Beloved</div><div><br></div><div>New Dragon and Wyrmprint:</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragon</div><div>5★ Prometheus (flame)</div><div><br></div><div>■Wyrmprint</div><div>4★ Entwined Flames</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div>From <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550124000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1550815140"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers, dragons, and wyrmprints below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured Adventurer</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
